Patrick Barlow https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_Barlow 0 Evan George Patrick Barlow (born 18 March 1947 in Leicester, Leicestershire) is an English actor, comedian and playwright. His comedic alter ego, Desmond Olivier Dingle, is the founder, Artistic Director and Chief Executive of the two-man National Theatre of Brent, which has performed on stage, on television and on radio.
